### List categories
# @name list_categories
GET https://localhost:5001/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

@firstCategoryId = {{list_categories.response.body.$.categories[:1].categoryId}}


### Get single category
GET https://localhost:5001/categories/{{firstCategoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}} 
